14 An act relating to developing the Department of Corrections’ community
15 restitution program
16 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
17 Sec. 1. COMMUNITY RESTITUTION; DEVELOPMENT;
18 IMPLEMENTATION
19 (a) On or before July 1, 2025, the Department of Corrections shall
20 reinstitute the Field Based Community Restitution Program, commonly
