7 (b) The Department of Corrections may enact policies limiting the number
8 of days ordered on a single mittimus and how many total work crew days an
9 offender may have outstanding at any time to be eligible for work crew. The
10 Department shall set the number of work crew days imposed under a single
11 mittimus to not less than 20 days or the total number that may be outstanding
12 on multiple mittimuses to not less than 60 days.
13 Sec. 2. EFFECTIVE DATE
14 This act shall take effect on passage.
